医生端AJAX接口

修改个人账户：
    每个参数都不是必须，即不传代表不修改
POST /doc/modify_account
request:
    name:           <string>
    title:          <string>
    specialty:      <string>
    description:    <string>
    department:     <int>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>   // 0 - 成功
    message:        <string>
}

上传个人头像
POST /doc/upload_portrait
request:
    portrait:       <image>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>
    message:        <string>
    path:           <string>
}

添加/修改医嘱
    请在模板文件中标明record_id所在位置
POST /doc/modify_advice
request:
    record_id:      <int>
    advice:         <string>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>
    message:        <string>
}

修改挂号状态 -- ( 如将‘未就诊’改成‘已就诊’ )
POST /doc/modify_status
request:
    record_id:      <int>
    status:         <int>   // 0 - 未就诊，1 - 已就诊， 2 - 需复诊
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>
    message:        <string>
}

获取时间表:
GET /doc/get_schedules
request:
    page:           <int>
    date:           <date format:yyyy-dd>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>,
    totality:       <int>,
    schedules:
    {
        <date format:yyyy-mm-dd>:      // 
        [
            {
                'id': <int>,
                'period': <int>     // 0 - 上午，1 - 下午
            }
        ]
    }
}

获取病人挂号列表：
GET /doc/get_records_bs
request:
    page:           <int>
    schedule_id:    <int>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>,
    totality:       <int>,
    patients:
    [
        {
            id:         <int>
            time:       <time format:mm-ss>,
            name:       <string>
        }
    ]
}

获取病人评价:
GET /doc/get_comments:
request:
    page:           <int>
    date:           <date format:yyyy-dd>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>,
    totality:       <int>,
    comments:
    [
        {
            id:         <int>,
            name:       <string>,
            content:    <string>
        }
    ]
}

获取病人医嘱:
GET /doc/get_advice:
request:
    page:           <int>
    date:           <date format:yyyy-dd>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>,
    totality:       <int>,
    advice:
    [
        {
            id:         <int>,
            name:       <string>,
            content:    <string>
        }
    ]
}

获取未添加医嘱的挂号记录:
GET /doc/get_null_advice:
request:
    page:           <int>
    date:           <date format:yyyy-dd>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>,
    totality:       <int>,
    advice:
    [
        {
            record_id:  <int>,
            user_id:    <int>,
            user_name:  <string>
        }
    ]
} 

获取消息:
GET /doc/get_messages:
request:
    page:           <int>
    date:           <date format:yyyy-dd>
    totality:       <int>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>,
    totality:       <int>,
    messages:
    [
        {
            id:         <int>,
            content:    <string>,
            time:       <timestamp>
            status:     <int>               // 3 - 未读, 4 - 已读
        }
    ]
}